General.Name: Indo Straits Tbk
General.Description: PT Indo Straits Tbk, together with its subsidiary, provides integrated marine engineering and logistics support services in Indonesia. The company's marine engineering services include lifting, dredging and reclamation, and marine pilling, as well as civil construction works; offshore supply services to oil and gas coal mining industries; and construction of jetty, breakwaters, marinas, and similar structures. It also provides marine logistic support services, such as coal barging and transportation support, and transshipment for coal mining companies; and mining contractor, as well as sea transportation services. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in North Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Indo Straits Tbk is a subsidiary of Straits Corporation Pte. Ltd.
